{"tid":883270,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點先知一個男仔係咪中意我？好亂呀","createTime":"2018-10-30T16:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T11:44:09.000Z","uid":103120,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"96fc36016dd6e83035ab13afdf2a26f6481cccf0","tid":883270,"uid":103120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T16:54:46.000Z","msg":"個男仔成日都揾我一齊温書，一個禮拜最少見4次，考試嘅話甚至係差唔多每日都見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試過單獨出去睇戲食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢温書嗰陣間唔中會用佢隻腳掂我隻腳，同埋行之後番黎嗰陣仲會摸我個頭，又用筆去篤我塊面，有幾次試過將成個人挨落我到但好快就起番身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最印象深刻係佢將個下巴放係我膊頭，我以為係啲女仔fd，但望一望發現係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我嗰陣嚇左一嚇<br />\n<br />\n亦有次佢不停咁叫我行埋去到，我問佢做咩，佢係咁叫我過黎先，但我堅持問佢想做咩，佢話想幫我鬢邊，不過最後我都拒絕左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋有次温書個陣我除低左件外套放係枱面，佢就由溫書開始嗰刻，反轉件外套咁著，又當件外套係枕頭咁攬住<br />\n直到温完書隔左6粒鐘先比番我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nps:佢自己都有帶外套<br />\n<br />\n有幾次過馬路或者有車仔係我附近嘅時候都會拉一拉我/撘住膊頭推我行快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最重點係佢成日會拎我手機黎睇入面啲野，我發現佢淨係睇我一個人嘅手機，其他人嘅唔會拎黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔知點解<br />\n<br />\n家下我地嘅朋友都以為我地拍緊拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但其實冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟佢係真係中意我定當我係絲打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n媽呀好亂呀"},{"pid":"d0d3e315861c7a91bec26145a536d36dec1b61a8","tid":883270,"uid":203576,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T16:55:57.000Z","msg":"除褲 叫佢含"},{"pid":"47c21f06e71fcdaad8e61b26aaf7aa5adbb257a9","tid":883270,"uid":145898,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T16:58:13.000Z","msg":"都幾肯定係鍾意你<br />\n因為我都有對住鍾意既女仔做過差唔多你講既全部野 但係唔知佢get 唔get 到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084efdc75ea3efeead9641ce1a3f888476c65396","tid":883270,"uid":53254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:00:51.000Z","msg":"含佢, 冇推開應該可玩埋屎眼"},{"pid":"c18ee391d8db3c3869c63c24b5c4e20158d88b99","tid":883270,"uid":161190,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:01:53.000Z","msg":"個問題係你仲唔仲意人哋"},{"pid":"a9b66318125edbdb297e1e74e6af8ac80e80a643","tid":883270,"uid":103120,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"47c21f06e71fcdaad8e61b26aaf7aa5adbb257a9","tid":883270,"uid":145898,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T16:58:13.000Z","msg":"都幾肯定係鍾意你<br />\n因為我都有對住鍾意既女仔做過差唔多你講既全部野 但係唔知佢get 唔get 到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:02:09.000Z","msg":"Get到嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我呢個A0乜都唔知嘅人都feel到有野佢點會get唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我都係唔肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56407b76772a499437161b8281c558bbdddd2e0b","tid":883270,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:02:12.000Z","msg":"去廁所時格劍"},{"pid":"ad399ac6036f6fac60be28c9797ddcadd1756ea4","tid":883270,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T17:02:22.000Z","msg":"當你係巴打"},{"pid":"d007f7187b86b711325d7701f3e887ab